  * Clean up CMakeLists.txt, drop Qt4 support

0.2.0 / 2014-10-19
==================

  * Release 0.2.0
  * simplify QT switching, use ENV
  * Use QString::fromLatin1() instead of QString::fromAscii()
  * Adapt the build system to handle Qt4 and Qt5
  * Improve FreeBSD support

